orge/ai_workflows/fix_metadata_codex.py)). Each task runs Gradle tasks against a worktree of this repo, appends a schema-validated metrics record, and — when invoked through [`forge/git_scripts/make_pr_*.py`](../forge/git_scripts/) — opens a PR for human review. See [forge/docs/architecture.md](../forge/docs/architecture.md). |\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge9/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/918-66d2149d/docs/FUNCTIONAL_SPEC.md:46:- A `stats/<groupId>/<artifactId>/<metadata-version>/stats.json` mirror of per-version metrics (dynamic-access call sites, coverage, lines of code, dependency information).\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge9/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/918-66d2149d/docs/FUNCTIONAL_SPEC.md:55:- Coverage collection (JaCoCo) and dynamic-access reporting per coordinate.\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge9/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/918-66d2149d/docs/FUNCTIONAL_SPEC.md:74:- `latest/badges.json` — badges shown in the README (libraries supported, tested versions, dynamic-access coverage, tested LOC).\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge9/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/918-66d2149d/docs/FUNCTIONAL_SPEC.md:84:1. **Add new library support** — generate a JUnit test suite, scaffold metadata, iterate until JVM-mode tests pass and dynamic-access metadata is collected.\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge9/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/918-66d2149d/docs/FUNCTIONAL_SPEC.md:87:4. **Improve coverage** of already-supported libraries by targeting uncovered dynamic-access call sites.\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge9/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/918-66d2149d/docs/DEVELOPING.md:319:  Output: `metadata/<group>/<artifact>/<version>/test/build/reports/dynamic-access/dynamic-access-coverage.json`\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge9/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/lo